public class FromStringLiteral
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.common.base.Function<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>

Function that uses standard EMF mechanism to create an instance of an EDataType from a String literal.

The apply(String) method calls EcoreUtil.createFromString(EDataType, String).
